description:
As a user of Shopline
  I want to update product's inventory
  So that I can keep inventory of those product in correct quantity
name: Admin update inventory API call Benchat send Email

steps.name: I am on Admin Login Page
I fill correct account email to email field
I fill correct account password to password field
I click on login button
I should see successful login
I check intercom message notification frame and click clear intercom message button
I check intercom message notification frame and click intercom message close button
I check new feature alert notification frame and click new feature alert close button
I check and click exclude products panel close button
I check and click no thanks button
I am on Basic Setting Page
I mark the value of shop name field as variable shop name
I click on basic info update button
I should be redirected to Dashboard Page
I am on Shop Login Layout V Two Page
I fill email to email field
I fill password to password field
I click on submit button
I should be redirected to Shop Home Layout V Two Page
I am on Inventory Page
I input "17th Product for Checkout" to search field
I should see row of product list
1st row of product list should contain "17th Product for Checkout"

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"17th Product for Checkout Published OFF 3000010Blue 1000000Add SetSaveRed 2000010Add SetSave","expectText":"17th Product for Checkout"}

steps.name: I should see apply search label
I click on 2nd set button
I click on 1st set button
I fill "0" to 2nd row of quantity field
I fill "0" to 1st row of quantity field
I click on 2nd save button
I click on 1st save button
1st row of product list should contain "0"

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"17th Product for Checkout Published OFF 0Blue 0Add SetSaveRed 0Add SetSave","expectText":"0"}

steps.name: I am on Shop Product Index Layout V Two Page
I hover over search icon
I input "17th Product for Checkout" to search field
1st kingsman product of products list should contain '17th Product for Checkout'

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"17th Product for CheckoutNT$10NT$100","expectText":"17th Product for Checkout"}

steps.name: I click on 1st kingsman product of products list
I should be redirected to Shop Product Show Layout V Two Page
I select variation option included "Blue" of variation selector
I should see notify when in stock button
I click on notify when in stock button
I should see alert
alert should contain "When product is back in stock, there will be email notification."

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"When product is back in stock, there will be email notification.","expectText":"When product is back in stock, there will be email notification."}

steps.name: I should see add to wishlist button on
I select variation option included "Red" of variation selector
I should see notify when in stock button
I click on notify when in stock button
I should see alert
alert should contain "When product is back in stock, there will be email notification."

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"When product is back in stock, there will be email notification.","expectText":"When product is back in stock, there will be email notification."}

steps.name: I should see add to wishlist button on
I am on Inventory Page
I input "17th Product for Checkout" to search field
I should see row of product list
1st row of product list should contain "17th Product for Checkout"

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"17th Product for Checkout Published OFF 0Blue 0Add SetSaveRed 0Add SetSave","expectText":"17th Product for Checkout"}

steps.name: I should see apply search label
I click on 2nd set button
I fill "10" to 2nd row of quantity field
I click on 1st save button
row of product list should contain "10"

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"17th Product for Checkout Published OFF 10Blue 0Add SetSaveRed 10Add SetSave","expectText":"10"}

steps.name: I wait for 100 seconds for mail sent
I am on Google Mail Page
I fill customer email to account field
I click on identifier next button
I should see password field
I input account password to password field
I check and click password next button
I should see search field
I input shop name to search field
I wait for 3 seconds for loading
I should see row of mail list
I click on row of mail list included 'your wishlist is back in stock'
